text:
Commerce Street, west from Bleecker Street, showing this Greenwich Village thoroughfare prior to demolition for the extension southward of Seventh Avenue. All of the foreground structures, with the exception of No. 286 at the left, will be removed for same. This will run in the line of Bleecker Street, tho crossing same at the right. Later views from this vantage point will be across this new thoroughfare.

1899

J. J. Corell, photo
P. L. Sperr Collection
